description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Within &lt;strong&gt;Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/strong&gt;, research is considered a critical component of a successful NHS provider organisation and there are a number of active on-going trials and service evaluations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Research trials are important to ensure that the best advice and treatments are being provided to patients. Southern Health has a core Research &amp; Outcomes Department which supports research across services throughout the organisation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role will be to govern the research team under aspects of administration related to research and service evaluations by:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role will be to govern the research team under aspects of administration related to research and service evaluations by:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working alongside the Research Portfolio Delivery Leads, the post holder will act as the person responsible for collating documentation for, and then assessing/issuing the capacity and capability of SHFT to participate in clinical trials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as the main point of contact for investigators and researchers for all queries relating to research governance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilising data reporting systems to produce performance data reports for Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supporting management and portfolio leads teams in providing a consistent approach to costing and pricing of research&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the person responsible for HR aspects relating to R&amp;D, including staff contracts, sickness reporting, induction and leaving procedure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With support from mangers, act as the person responsible for the maintenance of e-rostering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is not an exhaustive list and the Job Description and Person Specifications should be referred to for the full role requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Happy to Talk Flexible Working- &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;all requests for flexible and part time working will be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
